 that the colour scheme selected reflects the business and contributes to the connection with customers, whilst projecting a professional attitude.<\\/p><p>The website had to be targeted to provide interaction with current customers and anyone who wants to recharge, relax or find alternative ways to manage stress and anxiety.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"1411937\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a1315b7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/portfolio\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/AHAT-Logo.png\",\"id\":197},\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":\"\",\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"25\",\"right\":\"25\",\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":\"25\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\",\"_element_vertical_align\":\"center\",\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d33c044\",\"elType\":\"section\",\"settings\":[],\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"53fe9b2\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":100},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"3c56860\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"title\":\"User Personas\",\"align\":\"center\",\"title_color\":\"#333333\",\"typography_typography\":\"custom\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"3\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"3\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":false},\"text_shadow_text_shadow_type\":\"yes\",\"text_shadow_text_shadow\":{\"horizontal\":5,\"vertical\":5,\"blur\":5,\"color\":\"rgba(0,0,0,0.3)\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"heading\"},{\"id\":\"c14ea4a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>User Analysis research have identified the 2 main types of Users to be Treatment- and Training clients.<\\/p><p>Their goals were almost identical, with only slight variations:<\\/p><