 that it had served its purpose and that it was time to move on to a professional website presence.<\\/p><p>Audrey Hird Alternative Therapies requested that a business identity be created for them, which will encompass setting their corporate colours, creating a logo and developing a website that will provide their clients with a way to book treatments and\\/or training at a time of their choosing.<\\/p><p>The current website must be replaced by a responsive website, reflecting their business identity and conveying a smart and professional image of the business.<\\/p><p>The website need to act as the first point of contact with their customers, provide directions, contact form &amp; -details, connection to social media channels, an events calendar, a blog and ultimately be the main portal of booking appointments for customers.<\\/p><p>It was very important that the colour scheme selected reflects the business and contributes to the connection with customers, whilst projecting a professional attitude.<\\/p><p>The website had to be targeted to provide interaction with current customers and anyone who wants to recharge, relax or find alternative ways to manage stress and anxiety.<\\/p>\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"1411937\",\"elType\":\"column\",\"settings\":{\"_column_size\":50,\"_inline_size\":null},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"a1315b7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/wordpress\\/portfolio\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2019\\/07\\/AHAT-Logo.png\",\"id\":197},\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":\"\",\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"25\",\"right\":\"25\",\"bottom\":\"25\",\"left\":\"25\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_element_width\":\"inherit\",\"_element_vertical_align\":\"center\",\"image_size\":\"medium\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"d33c044\",