tfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Logo-768x768.png 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Logo-1024x1024.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" />											\n			<h2>User Personas</h2>		\n		<p>User Analysis research have identified the 2 main types of Users to be Treatment- and Training clients.</p><p>Their goals were almost identical, with only slight variations:</p><ul><li style=\"list-style-type: none;\"><ul><li>Need to see Treatment (<em>Training</em>), Duration &amp; Pricing information</li><li>Enquire about the availability of appointments and be able to reach out to the business via phone, email &amp; by submitting a contact form</li><li>Be able to book an appointment (<em>training class</em>) at a time suitable to them, without having to contact AHAT</li><li>Requires a confirmation email after booking their appointment and an email reminder before the scheduled appointment takes place.</li></ul></li></ul><p>Separate User Personas were created for Training - and Treatment customers.</p><p>Input from the customer themselves were used in the creation of these, as their previous website had no analytical functionality.</p>		\n										<img width=\"957\" height=\"902\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Persona1.jpg\" alt=\"User Persona image\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Persona1.jpg 957w, http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Persona1-300x283.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Persona1-768x724.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 957px) 100vw, 957px\" />											\n										<img width=\"957\" height=\"902\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Persona2.jpg\" alt=\"User Persona image\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/portfolio/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/AHAT-Persona2.jpg 957w, http://localhost/wordpress/por